description:
Qt Creator 13 open-source IDE is now available for download with offline and online installers for Linux on ARM, as well as various improvements. Here's what's new!

The post Qt Creator 13 Released with Offline and Online Installers for Linux on ARM appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: Qt Creator 13 Released with Offline and Online Installers for Linux on ARM
